('4256', '373', 'content_1_text', 'Our company adheres to a Quality Management System in accordance with ISO 9001 and API Q1.\r\n\r\nIts products follow the guidelines and are certified to API 6D, European Directive (PED) and ATEX. Products can be tested by other Third Party Agencies like Bureau Veritas, TÃV, RINA, Lloydâs Register, Stoomwezen and other. Design and manufacturing are carried out in accordance with the main international standards, i.e. ISO, API, ASME, ANSI, ASTM, NACE, BS, AFNOR, DIN and other.'),
