('4421', '400', 'description', '<h3>Description</h3>\r\nGate valves are mainly used to intercept the flow in the oil & gas and power generation plants.\r\nThey are installed both on-shore and off-shore, in the cryogenic and water treatment services.\r\n\r\n<h3>Design</h3>\r\naccording to API 600, ASME B16.34, API 602 - ISO 15761 - BS 5352\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Bolted bonnet and pressure seal design</li>\r\n<li>Outside screw and yoke</li>\r\n<li>Rising stem</li>\r\n<li>Flexible and solid wedge</li>\r\n<li>Parallel slide version</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFire Safe tested API 6FA, API 607, ISO 10497\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>Range of production</h3>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-4\">\r\n		<img src=\"http://sitindustrievalvometal.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/ball-valves_tabella1.png\" width=\"250px;\">\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-8\">\r\n<strong>BOLTED BONNET</strong>\r\n<table style=\"margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>ENDS</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"6\">R.F. - R.T.J. - B.W. - S.W. - NPT</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>CLASS</td>\r\n<td>150</td>\r\n<td>300</td>\r\n<td>600</td>\r\n<td>900</td>\r\n<td>1500</td>\r\n<td>2500</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>NPS (up | to)</td>\r\n<td>56\"</td>\r\n<td>48\"</td>\r\n<td>48\"</td>\r\n<td>24\"</td>\r\n<td>24\"</td>\r\n<td>12\"</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-4\">\r\n		<img src=\"http://sitindustrievalvometal.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/ball-valves_tabella1.png\" width=\"250px;\">\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-8\">\r\n<strong>PRESSURE SEAL</strong>\r\n<table style=\"margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>ENDS</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"6\">R.F. - R.T.J. - B.W.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>CLASS</td>\r\n<td>-</td>\r\n<td>-</td>\r\n<td>-</td>\r\n<td>900</td>\r\n<td>1500</td>\r\n<td>2500</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>NPS (up | to)</td>\r\n<td>-</td>\r\n<td>-</td>\r\n<td>-</td>\r\n<td>24\"</td>\r\n<td>20\"</td>\r\n<td>20\"</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-4\">\r\n		<img src=\"http://sitindustrievalvometal.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/ball-valves_tabella1.png\" width=\"250px;\">\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-8\">\r\n<strong>THROUGH CONDUIT GATE</strong>\r\n<table style=\"margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>ENDS</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"6\">R.F. - R.T.J. - B.W.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>CLASS</td>\r\n<td>150</td>\r\n<td>300</td>\r\n<td>600</td>\r\n<td>900</td>\r\n<td>1500</td>\r\n<td>2500</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>NPS (up | to)</td>\r\n<td>60\"</td>\r\n<td>48\"</td>\r\n<td>48\"</td>\r\n<td>24\"</td>\r\n<td>16\"</td>\r\n<td>16\"</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<small>All sizes and ratings available on demand.\r\nWe can supply gate valves with manual levers, gear operators, electric, pneumatic or hydraulic actuators.</small>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>Construction Materials</h3>\r\nValvometal can manufacture valves with all types of material complying with ASTM & ASME standards and in accordance to customer needs and specifications (NACE standard included).\r\nThe main casted and forged materials used are: \r\n\r\n<p><strong>BODY AND BONNET</strong>\r\nCasted or forged carbon steel, low temperature carbon steel, alloy steel, stainless steel, exotic alloy, etc.</p>\r\n<p><strong>TRIM</strong>\r\nForged or pressed carbon steel, low temperature carbon steel, alloy steel, stainless steel, exotic alloys, etc.</p>'),
