('4538', '77', 'body_0_text', 'Valvometal successfully delivered 36â ball valves to WEPCO for El-Hamra terminal project near Alexandria.\r\n \r\nOn the same plant the year before were already successfully installed 36â gate valves which are now running in the plant.\r\n \r\nEl-Hamra is one of the main port in Egypt. The installation of the 36â offshore pipeline was hadled by ENPPI to tie-in with the existing onshore facility at El-Hamra terminal.\r\n \r\nThe new pipeline is capable to handle the transportation of 1,000,000 SBPD and i twill extend for 500 m from El-Hamra onshore facilities till the coastal line, then extends off shore for 8500 m toward the tie-in point with the new SPM site located approximately 23 m deep underwater.\r\n \r\nThe new pipeline is supposed to load/offload oil between El-Hamra tanks and tankers. The installation of the new 36â pipeline starts from the tie-in to the main line of the discharge pumps, located inside the WEPCO onshore plant, some 500m far from the shore line till the tie-in with the new SPM.'),
